             depos'd, that they saw the prisoner at the Nags head on Snow Hill lend Foster and Cummins 40 s. on the Cloth, and they gave him a Note to repay it in a Month or forfeit the Cloth;</p>
               <p>which Note (sign'd by these two Evidences) was produced in Court. 
               <persName id="t17220228-17-person131">
                  Patrick 
                  Turner 
               <interp inst="t17220228-17-person131" type="surname" value="Turner"></interp>
